---
title: Creamy Cheese Tortellini with Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto and Spinach
description: Cheese-stuffed tortellini gets a royal treatment in tonight's speedy dinner! This slightly untraditional, lip-smacking rosé sauce uses sun-dried tomato pesto to pack a flavourful punch.
